<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Home</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-image: url('bg.jpg');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;


    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .navbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      background-color: #333;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .navbar a {
      color: #f2f2f2;
      padding: .5rem 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      width: fit-content;
      transition: .2s;
    }

    .navbar a:hover {
      scale: 1.5;
      color: rgb(65, 186, 231);
    }

    .container {
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: auto auto;
      background: linear-gradient(111.29deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.53) -1.83%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 109.95%);
      border: 1px solid rgb(211, 211, 211);
      backdrop-filter: blur(.8rem) saturate(180%);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(.8rem) saturate(180%);
      border-radius: 2rem;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #555;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #ffffff;
      
    }

    ul li:before {
      content: "âœ“ ";
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-right: 5px;
    }
    .area{
      display: flex;
      height: 70vh;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .profilearea{
      background-color: white;
      width: 35vh;
      display: flex;
      margin: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .logoarea{
      width: 10vh;
      height: 10vh;
      background-image: url('doc_logo-removebg-preview.png');

    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="navbar">
    <a class="active" href="#home">Home</a>
    <a href="/patients">Patient Details</a>
    <a href="/blood-requirement">Blood Requirement</a>
  </div>
  <div class="profilearea">
    <div class="logoarea">
      <img src="doc_logo-removebg-preview.png" alt="" width="100%" height="100%">      
    </div>
    <div class="textarea">
      <div id="name">
        Dr. <%= locals.user_data.fname%>  <%= locals.user_data.lname%>
      </div>
      <div id="designation">
        <%= locals.user_data.designation%>
      </div>
      <div id="institution">
        <%= locals.user_data.institution_name%>
      </div>
      <div id="place">
        Username : <%= locals.user_data.username%>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="area">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome to Your Doctor Portal</h1>
      <p>This web application empowers you to efficiently manage patient records, appointments, and your professional
        profile.</p>
      <p>With our platform, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>View, update, and organize patient information securely.</li>
        <li>Schedule, track, and manage appointments seamlessly.</li>
        <li>Receive real-time notifications for upcoming appointments.
        </li>
        <li>Access comprehensive patient medical histories and treatment plans.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Use the navigation bar above to explore and utilize the various features of the application.</p>
    </div>
  </div>


</body>

</html>